First of all set following things on Linux workstation/server

	• Set IP address
	• Set hostname
	• Set DNS
	• Set Search Domain
	



By running Realm discover command it will show the discovery 

#realm -v discover zohaib.lab

Check the following packages:

	• Oddjob
	• Oddjob-mkhomedir
	• Sssd
	• Adcli
	• Samba-common-tools